{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886494896,"sessionID":"ses_284ebb1d0ffeBv9YVKRFhZV4Mg","part":{"id":"prt_d7b1568a20011MQyhiabXKieTf","messageID":"msg_d7b154bb30015XgLayKn9AVYz2","sessionID":"ses_284ebb1d0ffeBv9YVKRFhZV4Mg","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Proposal: AgentCube CLI Toolkit (kubectl-agentcube)\n2: \n3: ## AR-020 ŌĆö CLI pack ÕæĮõ╗ż\n4: \n5: | Field | Value |\n6: |-------|-------|\n7: | **Module** | `cmd/cli` |\n8: | **Language** | Python |\n9: | **Size** | M (Medium) |\n10: | **Status** | Proposed |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## Purpose\n15: \n16: Implement a comprehensive command-line interface (`kubectl-agentcube`) for packaging, building, publishing, invoking, and checking status of AI agents against AgentCube or standard Kubernetes. This proposal delivers:\n17: \n18: 1. **`pack`** ŌĆö Validates and prepares agent workspace, generates Dockerfiles, manages metadata\n19: 2. **`build`** ŌĆö Builds container images from packaged workspaces (local Docker or cloud builds)\n20: 3. **`publish`** ŌĆö Publishes/deploys agents to AgentCube (AgentRuntime CR) or standard Kubernetes\n21: 4. **`invoke`** ŌĆö Invokes published agents with JSON payloads\n22: 5. **`status`** ŌĆö Checks deployment status and displays information\n23: \n24: The CLI provides developers with a unified tool for the complete AI agent lifecycle management, from local development to production deployment.\n25: \n26: ---\n27: \n28: ## Scope\n29: \n30: ### In Scope\n31: \n32: | Item | Detail |\n33: |------|--------|\n34: | **CLI Commands** | 5 subcommands: `pack`, `build`, `publish`, `invoke`, `status` |\n35: | **CLI Framework** | Typer with Rich markup for enhanced UX |\n36: | **Metadata Management** | YAML-based agent configuration with Pydantic validation |\n37: | **Docker Integration** | Docker SDK for building, pushing, and managing images |\n38: | **Kubernetes Integration** | Client-go via Kubernetes Python SDK for CRD operations |\n39: | **Multi-Language Support** | Python and Java agent packaging |\n40: | **Provider Abstraction** | Support for `agentcube` (AgentRuntime CR) and `k8s` (Deployment/Service) providers |\n41: | **Workspace Validation** | Structure validation, dependency processing, Dockerfile generation |\n42: | **Error Handling** | Consistent error patterns with verbose mode and traceback support |\n43: | **Progress Indicators** | Rich Progress spinners for long-running operations |\n44: \n45: ### Out of Scope\n46: \n47: - Interactive wizard mode for agent creation\n48: - Remote workspace synchronization\n49: - Multi-registry image mirroring\n50: - Built-in container registry\n51: - Hot-reload development mode\n52: - IDE integrations (VSCode/JetBrains plugins)\n53: - Web-based management UI\n54: - Automated testing framework for agents\n55: - Performance profiling tools\n56: - Cost estimation and billing integration\n57: \n58: ---\n59: \n60: ## Design\n61: \n62: ### Package Layout\n63: \n64: | Path | Role | Lines (est.) |\n65: |------|------|--------------|\n66: | `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping | ~80 |\n67: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version, exports `app` and runtimes | ~30 |\n68: | `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker | ~10 |\n69: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer app, all commands, error handling | ~350 |\n70: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass | ~60 |\n71: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` | ~20 |\n72: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` implementation | ~280 |\n73: | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` implementation | ~200 |\n74: | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` implementation | ~250 |\n75: | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` implementation | ~180 |\n76: | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` implementation | ~120 |\n77: | `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Services package docstring | ~15 |\n78: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataService` | ~180 |\n79: | `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | `DockerService` for image operations | ~220 |\n80: | `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | `KubernetesProvider` for K8s deployments | ~200 |\n81: | `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | `AgentCubeProvider` for AgentRuntime CR | ~180 |\n82: | `agentcube/operations/__init__.py` | Placeholder module docstring | ~10 |\n83: | `examples/hello-agent/main.py` | Example Python agent | ~40 |\n84: | `examples/math-agent/main.py` | Example math agent | ~60 |\n85: \n86: ### Architecture\n87: \n88: ```\n89: ŌöīŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöÉ\n90: Ōöé                     AgentCube CLI (kubectl-agentcube)                Ōöé\n91: Ōöé                                                                      Ōöé\n92: Ōöé  ŌöīŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöÉ  ŌöīŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöÉ  ŌöīŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöÉ  ŌöīŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöÉ Ōöé\n93: Ōöé  Ōöé    pack     Ōöé  Ōöé   build     Ōöé  Ōöé  publish    Ōöé  Ōöé   invoke    Ōöé Ōöé\n94: Ōöé  Ōöé  ŌöīŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöÉŌöé  Ōöé  ŌöīŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöÉŌöé  Ōöé  ŌöīŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöÉŌöé  Ōöé  ŌöīŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöÉŌöé Ōöé\n95: Ōöé  Ōöé  ŌöéPackRuntimeŌöé  Ōöé  ŌöéBuildRuntimeŌöé  Ōöé  ŌöéPublishRuntimeŌöé  Ōöé  ŌöéInvokeRuntimeŌöé Ōöé\n96: Ōöé  Ōöé 